description: Kyouko is a reckless girl who has eyes only for http://anidb.net/ch9538 [Yasuko]. She is in the same class as http://anidb.net/ch9537 [Akira] and is a member of the drama club. She has been dubbed as princess for her charm, and is also skilled in sewing, art, tennis and acting.
name: Ikumi Kyouko
